gw.api.webservice.pl.dataExtraction

Interface DataExtractionConstants.PLTemplateAttributes

  • Enclosing interface:
    DataExtractionConstants

    public static interface DataExtractionConstants.PLTemplateAttributes
    Template context attribute names, which can be referred to from within the template (Velocity/Gosu).

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String[] ALL_TEMPLATE_ATTRIBUTES
      Must contain all the Velocity attributes above.
      static java.lang.String ERROR_ATTRIBUTE
      Used to store any error messages

    • Field Detail

      • ERROR_ATTRIBUTE

        static final java.lang.String ERROR_ATTRIBUTE
        Used to store any error messages
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ALL_TEMPLATE_ATTRIBUTES

        static final java.lang.String[] ALL_TEMPLATE_ATTRIBUTES
        Must contain all the Velocity attributes above. This array is used internally to know what attributes to load into the Velocity context. Note: Excludes the 'error' attribute.
